67 SECTION 2.
68 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2025, and shall apply beginning with the
69 2025-2026 school year with respect to local education agencies and the 2025-2026 academic
70 year with respect to postsecondary institutions.
71 SECTION 3.
72 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
